#circuitbreakersg day 46

Braised pork buns 扣肉包🤤
Added yam and mushrooms (you can actually make vegetarian version too, 3rd & 4th pic is Yam n mushrooms)

Bun is from @noodleman678 It’s so soft and i like to eat it plain too🤣

Do you prefer fatty meat or lean meat? Fats is for sure for me but needa stay healthy 😂😭 Also had Long bean omelette and Stir-fry Sweet potato leaves.

#stayhome #jxeatshome
@hungry.girl.wanders omg i love to eat the bun itself too😍 haha
Love how fluffy that bun is! And fatty for sure!
@yimmyadventures oh yes. the mushroom is so juicy!!
Wow mushrooms sounds soo good with braised pork 🤤
Oooh now that is a good idea!!!
How nice that braised pork buns 😍
@hungryaffair omg i will make sure to drizzle somemore sauce the next time i have braised pork buns🤣
Love this so much! Like a good mix of fatty and lean for sure, and I’ll always dip the bun in the sauce too for added goodness 🤣
Wah love braised pork buns. Damn shiok 🤤
@floatsam_and_jetsam hope u get ur craving fix soon!
@thefoodadv omg same!! but i try to limit myself to max 3🤣🤣🤣😭😭
Omg I love Kong ba pau!!!!!! I can eat loads of this in a go HAAH
@numerounoeats 😅hope u can get ur craving fix soon!!❤️
Oh my ❤️ looks so delicious ❤️ drooling*
@hkfoodie_yamy 😍😍😍 do u prefer fatty or lean mean!
@jxeats Just Right! Not too fat or not too lean 😆 We are being too picky haha
@hkfoodie_yamy wahaha i have the same thoughts! u may wan to try pork collar. it has the right amount of fats and lean meat 🤣🤣
